game.name: The New Term Has Begun
game.description:
The Disney College has just started its new term today. Like many other students, your favorite princess Rapunzel is also excited to go to the college and meet her friends. But, the problem is that your favorite princess Rapunzel finds it difficult to choose a nice new school uniform. She tried a few options, but nothing could get her satisfied. Would you give your precious helping hands to the cute girl? Join The New Term Has Begun Game and be prepared to show off your excellent dress selection abilities!

Your objective in this brand new dressing game is to go through all the uniform options you find in her wardrobe and help you princess pick up the most suitable one. Do not forget to give your doll a matching makeover using the beauty accessories. There are plenty of hairstyles, hairpins, and dresses to select from. You can give her a warm outfit, a red colored long jacket with fur on the upper side with a combination of black jean, or a light green color sweater and a dark green color jean. 

You will also find a huge collection of elegant top and matching mini-skirts in her wardrobe. Give your princess a red color t-shirt and combine with a green color check mini-skirt! Dress her up with a blue color coat and a lovely matching blue mini-skirt in this html5 princess game! A light gray t-shirt and a black stylish jacket combined with a black color skirt will also give her a fantasy look. Mix and match all the options available in her wardrobe until you create the most impressing one!
